# TC37 : ObstacleDetectedBoost4
# Related normal-mode case : TC27_ObstacleDetected4
# Precondition : BoostMode, forward=true
# Action : right obstacle detected, front/left clear
# Expected : BoostMode 유지, CleanerDriver mode=boost 유지, no direction change
power
start
dust
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode boost
expect motorForward true
expect motorDirection FRONT
obstacle 0 0 1
expect mode BoostMode
expect cleaner on
expect cleanerMode boost
expect motor moving
expect motorForward true
expect motorDirection FRONT
exit
